money for a very high guaranteed return=E2=80=9D and the hedge funds were l=
ike =E2=80=9Cwhat=E2=80=99s the catch=E2=80=9D and EF Hutton was like =E2=
=80=9Cthe catch is that Donald Trump is generating the return from his loya=
l retail-investor fans=C2=A0and handing it to you in a shady and embarrassi=
ng way, also if you put in $50 million you have to talk to him about it,=E2=
