quisition Corp., the special purpose acquisition company planning to take T=
rump Media &amp; Technology Group public. =E2=80=9CThe Trump SPAC PIPE Is F=
ree Money,=E2=80=9D was <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/=
click/26431223.261630/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljb=
