lank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bot=
tom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; b=
ackground-color: #ccc;"> one Money Stuff headline</a>, which is sort of lik=
e a buy recommendation?=C2=A0And I suppose that if Trump=E2=80=99s bankers =
at =E2=80=A6=C2=A0it <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cli=
ck/26431223.261630/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzE4=
