p and offered me a slice of the deal, I probably would have subscribed for =
a bit.[1] But I see <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/clic=
k/26431223.261630/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyMi8wMS8yMC9idXNpbmVzc=
y90cnVtcC1tZWRpYS1pbnZlc3RvcnMuaHRtbA/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB5cd5df02" it=
