c;"> talked yesterday</a> about how Microsoft Corp. was able to buy Activis=
ion Blizzard Inc. at a discounted price because Activision had fallen into =
a deep reputational hole due to sexual misconduct allegations. =E2=80=9CWe=
=E2=80=99ll pay someone $20 billion to take our reputational risks away fro=
