at and pocket the difference.=E2=80=9D Which seems like a good bet! Microso=
ft=E2=80=99s situation right now is in some sense that it is the giant cash=
-rich tech company that is the=C2=A0<em>most efficient bearer of reputation=
al risk</em>.[4] Here, read these two sentences:</p><ol style=3D"list-style=
-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09<li style=3D"margin=
-bottom: 5px;">Facebook (sorry, Meta Platforms Inc.) just spent $69 billion=
 buying a gaming company with a controversial=C2=A0chief executive officer =
facing allegations involving a sexual misconduct scandal.</li>=09<li style=
=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Microsoft=C2=A0just spent $69 billion buying a gam=
ing company with a controversial=C2=A0chief executive officer facing allega=
tions involving a sexual misconduct scandal.</li></ol><p style=3D"margin: 1=
6px 0;">I submit that when you read the first sentence (which is not true) =
you were like =E2=80=9Cugh, Facebook, are there any depths to which they wi=
ll not sink,=E2=80=9D and got all mad at Mark Zuckerberg. When you read the=
 second sentence (which is true) you fell asleep after the word =E2=80=9CMi=
crosoft.=E2=80=9D Microsoft has an ability to throw a thick blanket of bore=
dom over scandals,=C2=A0<em>which is valuable</em>, and which it is now mon=
etizing.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Or, here, EF Hutton went out and s=
hopped this deal to hedge funds and was like =E2=80=9Cgive us some money fo=
r a very high guaranteed return=E2=80=9D and the hedge funds were like =E2=
=80=9Cwhat=E2=80=99s the catch=E2=80=9D and EF Hutton was like =E2=80=9Cthe=
 catch is that Donald Trump is generating the return from his loyal retail-=
investor fans=C2=A0and handing it to you in a shady and embarrassing way, a=
lso if you put in $50 million you have to talk to him about it,=E2=80=9D an=
d most of the hedge funds were like =E2=80=9Cyou know what, I don=E2=80=99t=
 need the money that badly,=E2=80=9D and some of them were like =E2=80=9Cye=
ah I can tolerate that sign me up.=E2=80=9D They=E2=80=99re getting sweet t=
erms, but they have to work for them.</p><table class=3D"liveintent-sponsor=
